{"tid":30872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺咁易走返高登既人都痴撚線正含家產","createTime":"2016-12-09T10:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T03:57:22.000Z","uid":187,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"269210f2bc197e55fd80023aed1089d8ea154961","tid":30872,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"林祖洩一直以黎<br />\n亂bam人 放sms 唔理5毛<br />\n<br />\n都算撚數啦 <br />\n喪心病狂到連hkg+都bam埋<br />\n仲要潛足一個月水無回應過<br />\n佢根本就唔會理民意！<br />\n想人一定要用佢官方app<br />\n原本仲想改都唔改咁<br />\n以為我地會硬食<br />\n<br />\n1125仲話自己屹立不倒<br />\n又屌人翻版野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講 我以前都好愛高登<br />\n甚至係到識到班痴線佬<br />\n但真係忍無可忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次佢收皮後<br />\n都無心反省無心改<br />\n係真係人走哂先跪低咋<br />\n<br />\n如果改2下就返去<br />\n真係不撚知所謂<br />\n一陣真係多人返<br />\n<br />\n首先lihkg會收皮<br />\n佢無人同佢爭人<br />\n你覺得佢會重視你咩屌你老母<br />\n到時佢迫你食官方app<br />\n你都吹佢唔脹呀 <br />\n仲有 咁撚無骨氣<br />\n第日唔會有連尼住同plus仔再比方舟你上！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次係佢條撚樣最接近收皮既一次<br />\n多人返去佢第日仲唔串過馬撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時真係無人收到佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b93514438d12177be95a05c52f73bae35550fe2","tid":30872,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"c6e9d406df2a055a52ce6dd18011e4b7e6a060df","tid":30872,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9284180d4d54d2c6a72dded67194aed144ce6ae","tid":30872,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"點都好啦.高登始終是我家,真心希望大家玩完識返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c